            </p>
            <div class="pt-4">
              <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-orange-600 text-white text-sm font-medium rounded-md">
                Recommended
              </span>
            </div>
            <ul class="text-sm text-left text-gray-600 space-y-2">
              <li>âœ“ Automatic trade sync</li>
